des:
Helo Mate products help you control home appliance.You can simply ask Alexa to turn on or turn off your plug.
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust your plug - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo.
After connecting Alexa to your Helo Mate products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Helo Mate" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register an account in our "Helo Mate" app;
(3). You need to have some Helo Mate devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Helo Mate" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Helo Mate" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Helo Mate" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Helo Mate", and you'll be navigated to "Helo Mate" login page;
(9). Input your Helo Mate account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa, turn on the plug.”
“Alexa, turn off the plug.”
